'''Finance Minister''' was a position within the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. [[Gahg]] held it in [[19 BBY/Legends|19 BBY]]. This high ranking bureaucrat was responsible for leading the [[Ministry of Finance (Galactic Empire)|Ministry of Finance]].

